snippet: Dr. Peter J. Ajemian pleaded guilty in federal court for his role in a widespread disability fraud involving workers at the commuter railroad.
abstract: Dr Peter J  Ajemian, orthopedist involved in widespread disability insurance fraud  involving dozens of Long Island Rail Road workers, pleads guilty.
lead_paragraph: Dr. Peter J. Ajemian pleaded guilty in federal court for his role in a widespread disability fraud involving workers at the commuter railroad.

headline.seo: Doctor Admits Faking Disability Claims for L.I.R.R. Workers
headline.main: Doctor Tells U.S. Judge He Created Fake L.I.R.R. Injury Claims
